{"tid":2076325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 公屋申請人隱暪持有1700萬物業　遭法庭判處監禁一個月緩刑一年","createTime":"2020-06-23T12:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T13:10:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b514793f85147341d4751e95c633df7ce95b864d","tid":2076325,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4734900/org/44a298491f5e2b48383aec28aede5cdb.jpg/wxM9UxfUM3k-6Uwywhw1RL4PjEZmRbY1oGZkP6BmZD8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4734900%2Forg%2F44a298491f5e2b48383aec28aede5cdb.jpg%2FwxM9UxfUM3k-6Uwywhw1RL4PjEZmRbY1oGZkP6BmZD8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=42b9bcba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該名公屋申請人分別在2015年填寫入息及資產申報表，以及在2017年於水泉澳邨辦事處填寫入伙聲明書時，均申報沒有物業及相關資產淨值。惟經調查後發現被告由2000年8月起，已經與他人聯權共同擁有一個位於紅磡海逸豪園的住宅物業，而該單位當時的估值約為1700多萬。以被告持有三分之一的業權計算，扣除未償還按揭貸款，被告所佔的房產淨值約為400多萬，已超逾15／16年度及16／17年度的公屋單身長者申請人總資產淨值限額的472,000元及484,000元，並不符合申請公屋的資格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/489665/公屋申請人隱暪持有1700萬物業-遭法庭判處監禁一個月緩刑一年\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F489665%2F%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E9%9A%B1%E6%9A%AA%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%891700%E8%90%AC%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E9%81%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E5%88%A4%E8%99%95%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Jb4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=2899b417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/489665/公屋申請人隱暪持有1700萬物業-遭法庭判處監禁一個月緩刑一年</a>"},{"pid":"605dc0528f88a9168230fec6273cc7227f723d57","tid":2076325,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.